snippet: Six current or former Dallas Cowboys players have been listed by prosecutors as potential witnesses for the intoxication manslaughter trial of the former lineman Josh Brent.
abstract: Prosecutors list six current or former Dallas Cowboys players as potential witnesses for intoxication manslaughter trial of former lineman Josh Brent; players may be called to testify about being at same nightclub as Brent on night of incident; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Six current or former Dallas Cowboys players have been listed by prosecutors as potential witnesses for the intoxication manslaughter trial of the former lineman Josh Brent.

headline.main: Cowboys Players Could Be Witnesses in Brent’s Trial
